data.description: Located conveniently in Boiling Springs, you are just blocks away to all Hwy 9 has to offer.  Built less than 2 years ago, this home is practically brand new.  Great starter or investment home.  This Floor plan is 3 BR/ 2.5 BA approx. 1617 sq. ft. with 1 car garage. this home has an upgraded kitchen with granite counter tops. Stainless Steel appliances. Vinyl flooring in specific areas. Kitchen has Breakfast Bar that opens up to the Dining and to the spacious Great room. Huge Master Suite and Master Bath.  Sit on the large patio and enjoy the privacy of the wood back yard.
